Type: Package
Package: invasimapr
Title: Workflow to visualise trait dispersion and assess invasibility
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
  person("Sandra", "MacFadyen", email = "macfadyen@sun.ac.za", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Utilities for assembling invader–resident interaction tensors, 
    computing trait-based competition kernels from distance matrices, 
    deriving environmental suitability kernels, calculating invasion fitness, 
    and summarising trait dispersion metrics. Includes helpers to predict 
    site × species responses for residents and simulated invaders.
